data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Disneyland is one of the world's most famous theme parks located in Anaheim, California. The park built by Walt Disney in 1955 is particularly popular with children. Disneyland, which has become the city's most important tourist destination, affects many people from 7 to 70. The park, which has many toys, is a center of attraction for animation and animation of cartoon characters. Disneyland is one of the places for those traveling in America to see.
